With this off-roader, Mercedes-Benz has tried to breathe new life into the sector.
Due to its exceptional characteristics, the Suv Glk will also be presented in an unconventional manner, which will be on display in the Mercedes-Benz showroom from 17 October.
Thus, the advertising drum that will accompany the appearance of the new model will also appear in a new dress, namely in the form of a 3D campaign – this is a novelty in the automotive sector in backward Italy.
A project with a maximum effort, which will be carried out in different chamois, which will occupy the central shopping mile of Milan, the Corso Como, by 15 November.
The first case will consist of the presentation of the car in form, whereby 3D glasses, which are distributed near the Corso Como, are intended to give the whole a special look: the new Suv will thus appear in its almost real dimensions as a three-dimensional model.
