With the help of the Elumina8 technology, the new Glk is illuminated in different moments in all its details, in order to sit back together as a whole.
Undoubtedly, it is Mercedes' concern with this advertisement to introduce a new kind of autoreklame into this rather stereotyped field.
But will it be able to attract the interest of future buyers? We will see it.
Now it is clear who the Italian hooligans are
